---
title: Old Bay-Spiced Trout & Sweet Potato Cakes with Tomato-Arugula Salad
description: Inspired by East coast crab cakes, this recipe calls on everyone's favourite Old Bay seasoning for serious flavour. Creamy sweet potato binds together flaky fish, sautéed aromatics and light panko breadcrumbs for tender pan-seared fish cakes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/old-bay-spiced-salmon-sweet-potato-cakes-a292aa2e.jpg
